    <p>Eater­ies are gear­ing up for the fes­tive sea­son by im­ple­ment­ing a host of mea­sures that will help them ac­com­mo­date cus­tomers in a safe way amid the coro­n­avirus pan­demic.</p>
    <p>Some restau­rants are hir­ing more staff to en­sure cus­tomers ad­here to safe man­age­ment mea­sures, while oth­ers are putting up more vis­ual re­minders – such as posters – of the Covid-19 reg­u­la­tions.</p>


